{"3486810": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "KimiMuzi", "steam_appid": 3486810, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/96a3a2038096cd0399a9ee57cbf7080e.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/96a3a2038096cd0399a9ee57cbf7080e.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/559a8b07e566e9aa68dcb90d206cb2b1.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/559a8b07e566e9aa68dcb90d206cb2b1.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以奇幻為主題的搞笑射擊遊戲！操作聖女羅緹，對抗襲來的獸人軍團。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被獸人打敗就會進入羞辱的特訓模式！只要撐過特訓，就能變得更強，狠狠教訓那些獸人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【角色介紹】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/6428a4d99bf6376664f239a02dd9eafb.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/6428a4d99bf6376664f239a02dd9eafb.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/71583a27e2f26823cc3289e9e4aed8d4.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/71583a27e2f26823cc3289e9e4aed8d4.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【主角（右側）】夏洛特·馮·波奇，暱稱羅緹。CV : 七海結理</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能夠展開結界來防禦魔物的聖女，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卻因未婚夫王子的厭惡，被發配到邊境，命令她去淨化魔之森林。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【獸人們（左側）】由籠罩世界的邪氣所生的魔物。肆虐了數百年，如今竟渴望被淨化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >牠們看中了羅緹的潛力，反過來決定鍛鍊她，讓她來淨化自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【遊戲介紹】</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/36e5b683d594eee706c16f7b9159df0f.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/36e5b683d594eee706c16f7b9159df0f.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >①使用魔法彈迎擊從畫面上方襲來的獸人軍團。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/630aa42057c7de9125051c61c53045c8.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/630aa42057c7de9125051c61c53045c8.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >②藍色的線是羅緹展開的結界，被破壞就會失敗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/f47226f7d6c4e01710edd10e371d6990.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/f47226f7d6c4e01710edd10e371d6990.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=261 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >③戰鬥失敗時，羅緹會被送去接受獸人的特訓，藉此變得更強。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/897233829f297052f3c2d26b1b45df5d.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/897233829f297052f3c2d26b1b45df5d.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >羅緹究竟能否成功淨化獸人，為他們帶來安息呢？</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/96a3a2038096cd0399a9ee57cbf7080e.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/96a3a2038096cd0399a9ee57cbf7080e.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=366 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/559a8b07e566e9aa68dcb90d206cb2b1.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/559a8b07e566e9aa68dcb90d206cb2b1.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=229 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以奇幻為主題的搞笑射擊遊戲！操作聖女羅緹，對抗襲來的獸人軍團。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被獸人打敗就會進入羞辱的特訓模式！只要撐過特訓，就能變得更強，狠狠教訓那些獸人！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【角色介紹】</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/6428a4d99bf6376664f239a02dd9eafb.avif?t=1754363669\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras_big/6428a4d99bf6376664f239a02dd9eafb.avif?t=1754363669 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3486810/extras/71583a27e2f26823